mawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03740/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03740/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03740/canvas/1/1ec23ece-a714-4a68-80c8-4895eda4482b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:34:08.064Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>According to production designer Mark Tildesley, Daniel Day-Lewis embraced the possibility of his pen leaking on him: “‘That pen was old, from a second hand shop, and started to leak. Everyone was concerned, but Daniel said, ‘No, this is the pen and, if the pen leaks, I’ll have a stain in my jacket – and that’s great!’” (Baughan, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW28269034 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.screendaily.com/features/how-phantom-thread-production-designer-mark-tildesley-nailed-the-films-intricate-details/5125746.article\"><u>How ‘Phantom Thread’ production designer</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03740/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:709.3405114401077,733.1628532974429,382.4495289367429,262.28802153432014"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03740/canvas/1/2ef792a6-0776-420c-ab31-ced2cbdaa366","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:34:21.715Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>PTA swears that the sound of the knife scraping on Alma’s toast was not amplified in any way (Xixax TV, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW238785617 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ro9bS5A-8j8\"><u>PHANTOM THREAD - London Q&amp;A</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03740/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1381.2113055181696,601.3728129205923,255.8277254374159,195.10094212651416"}}}]}]}]}